    "SUMMARY": "Giorgi Kochorashvili  () (Georgian: გიორგი ქოჩორაშვილი, romanized: giorgi kochorashvili; born 29 June 1999) is a Georgian professional footballer who plays as a central midfielder for Spanish club Levante UD and the Georgia national team."
